  "diagram_type": "stateDiagram",
  "code": "---\ntitle: \"Tolling.Network 2.0 — Transaction Lifecycle\"\n---\nstateDiagram-v2\n    [*] --> TollEvent: Vehicle uses facility\n\n    TollEvent --> TagLookup: Away agency reads tag/plate\n\n    TagLookup --> ChargeCreated: Tag found in TVL\n    TagLookup --> PayByPlate: No tag match\n\n    PayByPlate --> ChargeCreated: Plate lookup succeeds\n\n    ChargeCreated --> Submitted: Written to ledger\\n(private collection)\n\n    Submitted --> Acknowledged: Home agency confirms receipt\\n(return code 00)\n    Submitted --> Rejected: Validation failure\\n(return code 01-13)\n\n    Rejected --> [*]\n\n    Acknowledged --> Posted: Home agency posts\\nto customer account\n    Acknowledged --> NotPosted: Cannot post\\n(disposition D/I/N/S/T/C/O)\n\n    Posted --> Reconciled: Home agency writes\\nReconciliation record\\n(disposition P)\n\n    NotPosted --> Reconciled: Home agency writes\\nReconciliation record\\n(with rejection reason)\n\n    Reconciled --> CorrectionNeeded: Either agency\\nsubmits correction\n    Reconciled --> Settled: Included in\\nsettlement period\n\n    CorrectionNeeded --> Submitted: Corrected charge\\nresubmitted\n\n    Settled --> Paid: Off-chain payment\\nstatus updated\n\n    Paid --> [*]\n",
  "content_size": 1175,
  "collected_at": "2026-02-06T10:40:09.292781",
  "compilation_status": "success",
  "license": "other_source",
  "license_name": "Other Source (GitHub-based)",
  "compilation_error": "",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下Tolling.Network 2.0的交易全生命周期，从车辆通行到最终结算。起点应该是车辆使用收费设施这个事件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TollEvent",
        "Vehicle uses facility"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是TollEvent。接下来是不是要区分一下tag识别和车牌识别的路径？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TollEvent",
        "TagLookup",
        "PayByPlate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，外地机构先尝试读取tag或车牌，进入TagLookup环节。如果能匹配到TVL中的tag，就直接创建费用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TagLookup",
        "ChargeCreated",
        "TVL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了TollEvent到TagLookup，以及TagLookup成功匹配后进入ChargeCreated的分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TollEvent",
        "TagLookup",
        "ChargeCreated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "如果TagLookup没匹配到tag，就要走PayByPlate路径，用车牌去查，查到了还是能创建费用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TagLookup",
        "PayByPlate",
        "ChargeCreated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以PayByPlate是备选路径，最终也汇聚到ChargeCreated。那ChargeCreated之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PayByPlate",
        "ChargeCreated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ChargeCreated之后进入Submitted状态，写入账本，这属于private collection阶段。然后等待home agency的确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ChargeCreated",
        "Submitted",
        "private collection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认有两种结果对吧？return code 00是成功，01到13是失败？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Submitted",
        "Acknowledged",
        "Rejected",
        "return code 00",
        "return code 01 13"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。Acknowledged是home agency确认收到，Rejected是校验失败，直接结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Submitted",
        "Acknowledged",
        "Rejected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了Submitted的分叉。Acknowledged之后又有两个方向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Submitted",
        "Acknowledged",
        "Rejected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Acknowledged之后，如果能post到客户账户就走Posted，不能post的情况我们叫NotPosted，对应那些disposition D/I/N/S/T/C/O的场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Acknowledged",
        "Posted",
        "NotPosted",
        "disposition d/i/n/s/t/c/o"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Posted和NotPosted最终都要做reconciliation对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Posted",
        "NotPosted",
        "Reconciled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的。Posted走正常流程，disposition P；NotPosted要记录rejection reason。两者都进入Reconciled状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Posted",
        "NotPosted",
        "Reconciled",
        "disposition p",
        "with rejection reason"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Reconciled画好了。接下来是不是还有correction和settlement的分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reconciled",
        "CorrectionNeeded",
        "Settled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Reconciled之后，either agency都可以提交correction，进入CorrectionNeeded，修正后重新Submitted。正常的话就走Settled，进入结算周期。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reconciled",
        "CorrectionNeeded",
        "Settled",
        "Submitted",
        "either"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "CorrectionNeeded形成一个循环回到Submitted，Settled之后还有Paid状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CorrectionNeeded",
        "Submitted",
        "Settled",
        "Paid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Settled之后是Paid，off-chain payment状态更新，然后整个流程结束。这样交易生命周期就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Settled",
        "Paid",
        "off"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
